reviewText: My Grandpa loved these DVDs He watches them over and over again!!
Were given as gifts and seem to be satisfactory.

Mr gustan las peliculas de Jorge Negrete al igual que sus canciones, esyo es el estilo y voz, el no las compuso. Los mexicanos de esta epoca deberias familiarisarse con las peliculas y musica de este artista cantor. Se las recomiendo.
Jorge Negrete was great man in his time, all of his songs and movies were and will be the best ever.

Set consists of 2 disks, one of which is two sided. I have watched two of the films. They lack subtitles or fancy bonus features.  But they are stable, clear transfers of great vintage films with good sound.
